data.description: Welcome to this lovely, well-maintained home nestled on nearly half an acre in Dublin's charming Fair Acres neighborhood! This cozy yet spacious home offers 2 bedrooms and 2 full baths, providing comfort and convenience for you and your family. For those envisioning more space, there is ample room for expansion or adding additional bedrooms. The partially finished basement serves as a canvas ready for your personal touch to create living areas tailored to your unique needs and style. Notable highlights include the timeless hardwood flooring, a convenient two-car attached garage and one-car detached garage and/or storage building, a generous yard framed with a newly installed privacy fence and much more! To genuinely capture the character and charm of this home, you must see it in person! Don't miss your chance to make this house your new home. Schedule your showing today!
